vayuputra ( kannada : ವಾಯುಪುತ ರ ) is a 2009 indian kannada romantic action film directed by kishore sarja and produced by his brother , actor arjun sarja .   the sarja brothers launched their nephew chiranjeevi sarja through this film in the lead role .   the rest of the cast includes ambareesh , aindrita ray , ajay , sadhu kokila and several others .   the film is a remake of the blockbuster tamil film sandakozhi directed by n. linguswamy starring rajkiran , vishal and meera jasmine .   the original score and soundtrack for the film is composed by v. harikrishna .